{"tid":1968561,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子扮豪客劫屯門金舖，休班警門外路過制服","createTime":"2020-04-11T18:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T23:47:54.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"5933c7f7b44eb334e1737df30d21ca2eb503381d","tid":1968561,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"今日 （11日）下午4時許，屯門良景商場1樓一間金舖遇劫，兩名休班警途經時上前追截，最終成功拘捕一名40歲本地男子，屯門警區刑事調查總督察武少禧見記者交代案情。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/buGrqG0XuzlFtT31LCPdDoamumo=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/P55ININAPY3UNYCOVF27VDXYAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FbuGrqG0XuzlFtT31LCPdDoamumo%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FP55ININAPY3UNYCOVF27VDXYAU.jpg&h=5d26529e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200411/Y3TKGZ7NVGLQP7AINXIO5PZECU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200411%2FY3TKGZ7NVGLQP7AINXIO5PZECU%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W2o8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=1a81511e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200411%2FY3TKGZ7NVGLQP7AINXIO5PZECU%2F&h=ae204c8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200411/Y3TKGZ7NVGLQP7AINXIO5PZECU/</a>"},{"pid":"efd6f3dc5fe436ac8f4b9227867163624f4483f7","tid":1968561,"uid":118647,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:12:40.000Z","msg":"咁唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d534e8f29f7cd6e2d112023dbd695879d16a7bc8","tid":1968561,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:12:51.000Z","msg":"警方表示，案發前該名被捕男子曾進入涉案金舖假裝購買金鏈，其間有一名報稱是其妻子的30多歲中國籍女子陪同在側，兩人逗留約10分鐘後離開。再10分鐘後，該名男子獨自返回金舖，訛稱要分別試戴一條金鏈和鏈墜，職員拿出金鏈和鏈墜後，該男子突然放下一張屬於他人的信用卡，其後奪門而去。<br />\n<br />\n店員見狀，馬上跑出店舖並高聲呼救，與此同時有兩名休班警途經現場，目擊情況後上前追截約50米後成功制服該男子，成功起出被劫財物，總值約7.3萬元。其後警方經調查，發現該男子身上還藏有兩張屬於他人的信用卡。另外警方也在男子身上搜出一條贋品名錶，估計該名男子是借此假裝豪客，令店員放下戒心以便犯案。<br />\n<br />\n該名男子沒有黑社會背景，涉嫌「搶劫」及「盜竊」罪被捕，案件目前由屯門警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進，警方仍在追緝上述在逃女子，不排除稍後有更多人被捕。"},{"pid":"c919ba89b55e41a369af4cf886a5396de9c9105f","tid":1968561,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:14:11.000Z","msg":"唔係手足"},{"pid":"1dddb3075ac586b0bcd2b77f1430cabc11d4e955","tid":1968561,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:15:39.000Z","msg":"警方又指，所檢獲的兩張信用卡相信為真卡，並屬於另外兩名男子，並指涉案的金鏈及鏈咀的總值約為7.3萬港元，又指兩名涉案的男女在第一次進入店內時聲稱為夫婦關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123164421261.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123164421261.jpeg&h=408982a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123164568842.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123164568842.jpeg&h=5f4187aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123164778711.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123164778711.jpeg&h=2fe599c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123164851462.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123164851462.jpeg&h=c637e354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123164972994.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123164972994.jpeg&h=057f0a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200411/_2020041123165161985.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200411%2F_2020041123165161985.jpeg&h=dd6cbb4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d388e69653038f78ad77c92a4a83ec32045b48e0","tid":1968561,"uid":14494,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"基本野啦, 咁都要開記招<br />\n我自動呼吸緊又洗唔洗公告天下?"},{"pid":"9e2310a21ad8e438ea4a10fa5dba0dde0e832e79","tid":1968561,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"不排除稍後有更多人被捕<br />\n<br />\n有無得查都會見呢句，唯獨無可疑就無呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31634e71f0c443c4b5d0deafb366ded0f3ae71a8","tid":1968561,"uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:53.000Z","msg":"咁無大志，竟然去打劫屯門仲要良景呢啲地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee6aaacd0ef4d4ff10acc5c863c7833ccc8898c","tid":1968561,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:57.000Z","msg":"香港太多差佬"},{"pid":"0731217a2775b2ad9935ce0e10d3ca9e32ca0225","tid":1968561,"uid":150483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e2310a21ad8e438ea4a10fa5dba0dde0e832e79","tid":1968561,"uid":264245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"不排除稍後有更多人被捕<br />\n<br />\n有無得查都會見呢句，唯獨無可疑就無呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:18:18.000Z","msg":"根本得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣都驚過一驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔關抗爭事"},{"pid":"db9c63233ec7f1